<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #343a40;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .error-code {
            font-size: 12rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #dee2e6;
            letter-spacing: -8px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-shadow: 4px 4px 0px #adb5bd;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .error-code::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: #dee2e6;
            left: 0;
            bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .error-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #495057;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4263eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(66, 99, 235, 0.2);
        }
        
        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: #3b5bdb;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(66, 99, 235, 0.3);
        }
        
        .lost-icon {
            font-size: 6rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            color: #4263eb;
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(0px);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0px);
            }
        }
        
        .bg-shapes div {
            position: absolute;
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0.1;
        }
        
        .bg-shapes .circle {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #4263eb;
            top: 10%;
            left: 10%;
        }
        
        .bg-shapes .square {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background-color: #4263eb;
            bottom: 20%;
            right: 15%;
            transform: rotate(15deg);
        }
        
        .bg-shapes .triangle {
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-left: 75px solid transparent;
            border-right: 75px solid transparent;
            border-bottom: 130px solid #4263eb;
            top: 60%;
            left: 15%;
            transform: rotate(-20deg);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="bg-shapes">
            <div class="circle"></div>
            <div class="square"></div>
            <div class="triangle"></div>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
        <h2 class="error-title">Page Not Found</h2>
        <p class="error-message">Oops! The page you are looking for might have been removed, had its name changed, or is temporarily unavailable.</p>
        
        
        <a href="../home" class="home-button">Return to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>